%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20at%20Cutter%20Laboratories%20panicked%20many%20parents%20and%20the%20vaccine%20was%20pulled%20from%20the%20market%20on%20April%2027%2C%201955.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20after%20a%20massive%20effort%20to%20recheck%20all%20the%20vaccines%20confirmed%20they%20were%20safe%20to%20use%2C%20immunization%20resumed%20on%20May%2015%2C%201955.%20Worldwide%2C%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20children%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fslate.com%2Ftechnology%2F2021%2F02%2Fcutter-incident-polio-vaccine-drive-history.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereceived%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20vaccine.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EElvis%20got%20the%20vaccine%20backstage%20during%20the%20%26quot%3BEd%20Sullivan%20Show.%26quot%3B%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22elvis%20presley%20receives%20polio%20vaccine%20from%20a%20man%20while%20a%20woman%20stands%20nearby%20helping%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6069ec5fa7d803001963ea95%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221528%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOct.%2028%2C%201956%3A%20Elvis%20Presley%20receives%20the%20polio%20vaccine%20in%20New%20York%20City.%3Cp%3EAP%20Photo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20people%20were%20hesitant%20to%20have%20their%20children%20vaccinated%2C%20Elvis%20may%20have%20helped%20persuade%20them.%20After%20he%20got%20the%20jab%20in%20the%20fall%20of%201956%2C%20many%20followed%20suit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWithin%20six%20months%2C%2080%25%20of%20America's%20youngest%20generation%20were%20vaccinated%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scientificamerican.com%2Farticle%2Fhow-elvis-got-americans-to-accept-the-polio-vaccine%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EScientific%20American%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20in%202021.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOther%20celebrities%2C%20including%20Louis%20Armstrong%20and%20Ella%