C%22Ad-supported%20subscriptions%20are%20becoming%20more%20common%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22555%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e255c1e2-fa39-44d0-8d49-eae8cb85b06f%5C%22%3EViewers'%20tolerance%20for%20ads%20will%20be%20increasingly%20tested%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EStreamers%20that%20dipped%20a%20toe%20in%20the%20ad%20space%20are%20looking%20to%20wade%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ad%20load%20%E2%80%94%20or%20ad%20volume%20per%20hour%20of%20entertainment%20%E2%80%94%20has%20crept%20up%20over%20the%20past%20year%2C%20according%20to%20the%20measurement%20firm%20MediaRadar.%20There%20was%20an%20average%20of%20six%20minutes%20of%20ads%20per%20hour%20in%20September%20across%20eight%20leading%20ad-supported%20streamers%2C%20up%20by%209%25%20from%20January%202023%2C%20when%20Netflix%20and%20Disney%20had%20just%20entered%20the%20ad-supported%20game.%20That's%20still%20far%20lower%20than%20cable%2C%20where%20ad%20loads%20can%20push%20an%20eye-watering%2015%20minutes%20or%20more%20an%20hour.%20Viewers%20are%20also%20more%20likely%20to%20tolerate%20ads%20in%20live%20sports%20because%20people%20are%20used%20to%20them%20being%20part%20of%20that%20content.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22731%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22(L-R)%20Ryan%20Fitzpatrick%2C%20Charissa%20Thompson%20and%20Tony%20Gonzalez%20attend%20Amazon%20debuts%20Inaugural%20Upfront%20Presentation%20at%20Pier%2036%20on%20May%2014%2C%202024%20in%20New%20York%20City.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F667c5a66d1c84a0eaca80aff%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERyan%20Fitzpatrick%2C%20Charissa%20Thompson%2C%20and%20Tony%20Gonzalez%20host%20Amazon%20Prime%20Video's%20%26quot%3BThursday%20Night%20Football.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ESlaven%20Vlasic%2FGetty%20Images%20for%20Amazon%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwarner-bros-discovery-increase-streaming-ads-max-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWarner%20Bros.%20Discovery%3C%2Fa%3E%20recently%20said%20they'd%20start%20showing%20more%20ads%20to%20their%20streaming%20viewers%20in%202025%2C%20while%20emphasizing%20that%20their%20ad%20loads%20were%20lower%20than%20their%20competitors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20the%20ad-load%20side%2C%20we%20are%20light%2C%26quot%3B%20WBD's%20streaming%20chief%2C%20JB%20Perrette%2C%20said%20of%20the%20streamer%20Max%20during%20the%20company's%20third-quarter%20earnings%20call.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20a%20very%20light%20ad%20load%20compared%20to%20everyone%20else%20in%20the%20market%2C%20so%20there's%20room%20to%20grow%20on%20the%20capacity%20side.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20industry%20consensus%20is%20that%20streaming%20ad%20loads%20won't%20become%20a%20throwback%20to%20cable%2C%20though%20%E2%80%94%20at%20least%20not%20anytime%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20one%20thing%2C%20it's%20a%20buyer's%20market.%20Amazon%20flooded%20the%20market%20with%20ad%20inventory%2C%20which%20depressed%20ad%20prices%20for%20everyone.%20Streamers%20aren't%20incentivized%20to%20add%20too%20much%20more%20ad%20inventory%20because%20it'll%20just%20drive%20the%20price%20down%20more.%20Some%20advertisers%20are%20also%20wary%20of%20annoying%20viewers%20who%20are%20still%20getting%20used%20to%20seeing%20ads%20in%20streaming.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20supply%20has%20grown%20significantly%20over%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Maureen%20Bosetti%2C%20the%20chief%20investment%20officer%20for%20Mediabrands.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20created%20a%20marketplace%20for%20marketers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMakers%20of%20streaming%20video%20ads%20are%20also%20becoming%20more%20ambitious.%20It's%20not%20enough%20for%20an%20ad%20to%20be%20seen%20%E2%80%94%20they'll%20try%20to%20get%20viewers%20to%20take%20action%2C%20whether%20by%20clicking%20a%20QR%20code%20or%20dropping%20a%20featured%20product%20in%20their%20shopping%20cart.%20These%20interactive%20ads%20could%20get%20higher%20price%20tags%20at%20a%20time%20when%20streaming%20ad%20prices%20have%20come%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20a%20consumer%2C%20I'm%20seeing%20more%20of%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Jessica%20Brown%2C%20a%20managing%20director%20of%20digital%20investment%20at%20GroupM%2C%20said%20of%20interactive%20streaming%20ads.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20getting%20more%20pitches%20from%20the%20streaming%20partners.%20You%20can%20measure%20success%20in%20a%20different%20way.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWarner%20Bros.%20Discovery%20recently%20rolled%20out%20two%20such%20formats.%20%26quot%3BShop%20with%20Max%26quot%3B%20identifies%20items%20in%20TV%20shows%20and%20films%20and%20matches%20them%20with%20relevant%20advertiser%20products%20that%20viewers%20can%20shop%20while%20they%20watch.%20%26quot%3BMoments%26quot%3B%20uses%20AI%20to%20figure%20out%20themes%2C%20sentiments%2C%20and%20on-screen%20elements%20that%20line%20up%20tonally%20with%20the%20advertiser's%20message.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFubo%20recently%20announced%20four%20ad%20formats%2C%20including%20ones%20that%20show%20trivia%20questions%20or%20polls%20and%20product%20carousels.%20Fubo%20said%20such%20ads%20made%20people%2047%25%20more%20likely%20to%20purchase%20something%20compared%20with%20standard%20video%20ads.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20big%20objective%20we%20have%20is%20to%20make%20a%20majority%20of%20ads%20have%20some%20form%20of%20interactive%20or%20engaging%20feature%2C%26quot%3B%20Krishan%20Bhatia%2C%20an%20NBCUniversal%20exec%20who%20was%20hired%20by%20Amazon%20to%20lead%20its%20Prime%20Video%20ads%20push%2C%20said%20at%20a%20recent%20event.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20brands%20love%20about%20it%20is%20not%20just%20the%20fact%20that%20you%20generate%20a%20potential%20purchase%20off%20it%20but%20people%20are%20spending%20more%20time%20with%20your%20brands.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bus