nd%20year.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fmadhuri-dixit-rents-her-office-space-in-mumbai-for-rs-3-lakh-per-month-report%2Farticleshow%2F116379597.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Reverse%20Gear%20To%20Overdrive%3A%20Ajit%20Doval's%20Top%20China%20Meet%20To%20Boost%20Border%20Talks%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia%20and%20China%20have%20shown%20a%20sudden%20zeal%20to%20improve%20ties%20since%20the%20disengagement%20along%20the%20Line%20of%20Actual%20Control%20a%20little%20over%20a%20month%20ago.%20The%20relationship%20between%20the%20two%20most%20populous%20nations%20in%20the%20world%20was%20on%20reverse%20gear%20since%20the%20military%20stand-off%20in%20Ladakh%20more%20than%20four%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20since%20November%20the%20momentum%20has%20boomeranged%20and%20seems%20to%20be%20on%20overdrive%20-%20almost%20as%20though%20both%20sides%20want%20to%20make%20up%20for%20the%20time%20lost%20since%202020.%20New%20Delhi%20and%20Beijing%20understand%20well%20that%20for%20Asia%20to%20see%20lasting%20peace%2C%20the%20two%20Asian%20giants%20must%20lead%20the%20way.%20Nowhere%20is%20there%20a%20better%20start%20to%20this%2C%20than%20to%20find%20a%20solution%20to%20the%20boundary%20issue.%20And%20so%2C%20both%20sides%20seem%20to%20have%20made%20this%20a%20priority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENational%20Security%20Adviser%20Ajit%20Doval%20will%20be%20meeting%20Chinese%20Foreign%20Minister%20Wang%20Yi%20on%20Wednesday%20for%20a%20top-level%20meet%20to%20discuss%20the%20boundary%20issue.%20Though%20there%20has%20been%20no%20confirmation%20of%20this%20meeting%20from%20New%20Delhi%20yet%2C%20Beijing%20has%20said%20so%20in%20a%20foreign%20ministry%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChinese%20Foreign%20Minister%20Wang%20Yi%20and%20Indian%20National%20Security%20Adviser%20Ajit%20Doval%20will%20meet%20on%20Wednesday%20in%20Beijing%20to%20discuss%20the%20China-India%20boundary%20question%2C%26quot%3B%20Chinese%20Foreign%20Ministry%20spokesperson%20Lin%20Jian%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20agreed%20by%20China%20and%20India%2C%20Wang%20Yi%20and%20Ajit%20Doval%20will%20hold%20the%2023rd%20meeting%20of%20Special%20Representatives%20for%20China-India%20boundary%20question%20in%20Beijing%20on%20December%2018%2C%26quot%3B%20Chinese%20Ambassador%20Xu%20Feihong%20said%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20would%20be%20the%20first%20such%20meeting%20in%20five%20years%20-%20the%20last%20one%20being%20held%20in%20New%20Delhi%20in%20December%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20their%20first%20meeting%20more%20than%20a%20decade%20ago%2C%20both%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20Chinese%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20had%20given%20importance%20to%20finding%20a%20solution%20for%20effective%20border%20management%2C%20and%20the%20meeting%20in%20December%202019%20was%20the%2022nd%20meeting%20in%20the%20series%20of%20discussions%20to%20find%20a%20solution%20to%20settle%20any%20differences%20along%20the%20more-than%204%2C000%20km%20Line%20of%20Actual%20Control%20or%20LAC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20LAC%20has%20no%20clear%20demarcations%20and%20both%20sides%20have%20their%20differences%20in%20understanding%20of%20where%20the%20boundary%20lies%20in%20the%20harsh%20and%20arguably%20most%20difficult%20terrain%2C%20which%20span%20the%20highest%20mountain%20ranges%20in%20the%20world%20-%20The%20Himalayas.%20The%20border%2C%20originally%20between%20India%20and%20Tibet%20is%20now%20considered%20the%20boundary%20between%20India%20and%20China%20after%20Tibet's%20takeover%20by%20China%20in%201959.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20sides%20have%2C%20on%20several%20occasions%2C%20seen%20military%20face-offs%20by%20border%20patrol%20parties%2C%20each%20having%20their%20understanding%20of%20where%20exactly%20the%20boundary%20lies%20-%20which%20point%20on%20the%20mountain%2C%20valley%20or%20rivers%20mark%20or%20indicate%20the%20LAC.%20Though%20there%20are%20buffer%20zones%20created%20at%20several%20points%20along%20the%20LAC%2C%20even%20there%2C%20differences%20often%20crop%20up%20in%20how%20each%20side%20demarcates%20the%20boundary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20find%20a%20solution%20to%20this%2C%20India%20and%20China%20had%20started%20boundary%20talks%2C%20but%20all%20of%20that%20came%20to%20a%20grinding%20halt%20after%20the%20deadly%20clashes%20between%20the%20two%20armies%20in%202020%20in%20Galwan%20Valley%20in%20Ladakh%2C%20which%20saw%20soldiers%20from%20both%20sides%20killed%20in%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20more%20than%20four%20years%20of%20diplomacy%20and%20dialogue%20at%20the%20military%20and%20diplomatic%20levels%20for%20both%20sides%20to%20disengage%20-%20an%20agreement%20for%20which%20was%20reached%20in%20October%20this%20year%2C%20culminating%20is%20a%20rare%20formal%20meeting%20-%20also%20the%20first%20in%20five%20years%20-%20between%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20Chinese%20President%20Xi%20Jinping.%20The%20meeting%20took%20place%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20BRICS%20summit%20in%20Russia.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734378060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fk3h4vjd4_ajit-doval-wang-yi-ians_625x300_17_December_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Freverse-gear-to-overdrive-ajit-dovals-top-china-meet-to-boost-border-talks-7264275%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20and%20China%20have%20shown%20a%20sudden%20zeal%20to%20improve%20ties%20since%20the%20disengagement%20along%20the%20Line%20of%20Actual%20Control%20a%20little%20over%20a%20month%20ago.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Iran%20pauses%20controversial%20new%20dre