'%20Air%20Quality)%20of%20the%20%C2%A0GRAP%20schedule%20(issued%20on%2013.12.2024)%20in%20the%20entire%20NCR%2C%20with%20immediate%20effect%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20schools%20in%20Noida%20will%20start%20from%209%20am%20tomorrow%20due%20to%20severe%20cold%20and%20air%20pollution%2C%20operating%20in%20a%20hybrid%20mode.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat's%20Allowed%20And%20What's%20Not%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EStop%20entry%20of%20truck%20traffic%20into%20Delhi.%20Ban%20on%20construction%20and%20demolition%20activities%20for%20linear%20public%20projects%20such%20as%20highways%2C%20roads%2C%20flyovers%2C%20overbridges%2C%20power%20transmission%2C%20pipelines%2C%20telecommunication%20etc.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20government%20can%20discontinue%20physical%20classes%2C%20including%20Classes%20Vl%20-%20lX%20and%20Class%20Xl.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20government%20is%20to%20decide%20on%20allowing%20public%2C%20municipal%20and%20private%20offices%20to%20work%20on%2050%25%20strength%20and%20the%20rest%20to%20work%20from%20home.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EState%20governments%20may%20consider%20additional%20emergency%20measures%20like%20the%20closure%20of%20colleges%2Feducational%20institutions%20and%20closure%20of%20non-emergency%20commercial%20activities%2C%20permitting%20the%20running%20of%20vehicles%20on%20the%20odd-even%20basis%20of%20registration%20numbers%20etc.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EChildren%2C%20the%20elderly%20and%20those%20with%20respiratory%2C%20cardiovascular%2C%20cerebrovascular%2C%20or%20other%20chronic%20diseases%20to%20avoid%20outdoor%20activities%20and%20stay%20indoors.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBan%20on%20all%20construction%20and%20demolition%20activities%2C%20including%20public%20projects%20such%20as%20highways%20and%20flyovers%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fair-quality-panel-re-imposes-grap-3-restrictions-in-delhi-ncr-hybrid-mode-