0Rashtra%20Samithi%20or%20BRS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20on%20November%207%2C%20he%20said%20he%20was%20ready%20to%20face%20any%20inquiry.%C2%A0%26quot%3BIt%20is%20the%20governor's%20discretion.%20I%20have%20no%20objection%20if%20the%20governor%20gives%20permission%20for%20prosecution.%20We%20welcome%20it.%20We%20are%20ready%20for%20any%20inquiry%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20October%20this%20year%2C%20the%20Anti-Corruption%20Bureau%20had%20sought%20Telangana%20Governor%20Jishnu%20Dev%20Varma's%20nod%20to%20investigate%20KTR%20in%20the%20Formula%20E%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20former%20Municipal%20Administration%20and%20Urban%20Development%20principal%20secretary%20Arvind%20Kumar%20has%20admitted%20transferring%20Rs%2055%20crore%20to%20the%20event%20organisers%20on%20the%20verbal%20orders%20of%20the%20former%20minister%20who%20held%20the%20portfolio.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20irregularities%20in%20the%20transfer%20were%20multiple.%20Not%20only%20was%20the%20transfer%20made%20on%20verbal%20orders%2C%20it%20circumvented%20the%20cabinet%20approval%20and%20was%20done%20after%20elections%20were%20announced%20in%20Telangana%20without%20taking%20permission%20of%20the%20Election%20Commission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20also%20been%20alleged%20that%20the%20payment%20was%20made%20in%20pounds%20without%20the%20clearance%20of%20the%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Rao%2C%20who%20is%20also%20known%20as%20KTR%2C%20also%20held%20the%20Industry%20portfolio%20under%20the%20previous%20government%20headed%20by%20his%20father%20and%20BRS%20chief%20K%20Chandrashekar%20Rao.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20conduct%20seasons%20nine%2C10%2C11%20and%2012%20of%20the%20Formula%20E%20Race%2C%20the%20Municipal%20Administration%20and%20Urban%20Development%20department%20or%20MAUD%2C%20had%20signed%20a%20tripartite%20agreement%20with%20Formula%20E%20Organisers%20(FEO)%20and%20Ace%20Nxt%20Gen%20Pvt%20limited%20in%20202