ansode%2C%20Dilip%20Walse%20Patil%20and%20Anil%20Patil%20have%20been%20dropped.%20The%20corresponding%20number%20from%20the%20BJP%20and%20Eknath%20Shinde's%20Shiv%20Sena%20are%20three%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20dropped%20Ravindra%20Chavan%2C%20Sudhir%20Mungantiwar%20and%20Vijaykumar%20Gavit%20while%20the%20Sena%20has%20kept%20out%20Tanaji%20Sawant%2C%20Abdul%20Sattar%20and%20Deepak%20Kesarkar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChhagan%20Bhujbal%20has%20openly%20declared%20that%20he%20would%20not%20attend%20the%20assembly%20session%20any%20more%20and%20will%20return%20to%20Nashik%2C%20saying%20he%20has%20been%20disappointed.%20He%20also%20said%20he%20has%20been%20offered%20a%20Rajya%20Sabha%20seat%20but%20accepting%20it%20now%20will%20%26quot%3Bnot%20be%20fair%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20voters%20of%20Yeola.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20big%20leader%20dropped%2C%20Sudhir%20Mungantiwar%2C%20has%20contradicted%20Chief%20Minister%20Devendra%20Fadnavis's%20claim%20that%20he%20was%20dropped%20after%20a%20%26quot%3Blong%20discussion%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20had%20a%20long%20discussion%20with%20Sudhir%20Mungantiwar%20on%20the%20expansion%20of%20the%20cabinet.%20If%20he%20does%20not%20get%20a%20ministerial%20berth%2C%20there%20is%20a%20possibility%20that%20he%20will%20be%20given%20some%20big%20responsibility%20by%20the%20party%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Fadnavis%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Mungantiwar%20refuted%20the%20claim%2C%20saying%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20did%20not%20have%20a%20long%20discussion%20with%20him%20about%20the%20ministerial%20post.%20They%20spoke%20only%20spoke%20on%20the%20day%20of%20the%20expansion.%20Mr%20Fadnavis%20and%20state%20BJP%20chief%20Chandrashekhar%20Bawankule%20had%20said%20that%20his%20name%20was%20on%20the%20list%20of%20ministers%20the%20day%20before%20the%20cabinet%20expansion%2C%20but%20it%20turned%20out%20otherwise%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20others%20who%20were%20apparently%20in%20the%20running%20for%20a%20cabinet%20berth%20but%20ended%20up%20empty-handed.%20The%20Sena%20especially%20is%20facing%20backlash%2C%20with%20one%20of%20its%20MLAs%2C%20Narendra%20Bhondekar%2C%20having%20already%20quit%20party%20posts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVijay%20Shivtare%2C%20the%20MLA%20from%20Purandar%2C%20said%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bnot%20sad%20over%20ministership%2C%20but%20the%20treatment%20meted%20out%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20three%20leaders%20didn't%20communicate%20properly.%20I%20will%20not%20take%20ministership%20even%20if%20given%20after%202.5%20years%2C'%20he%20told%20reporters%2C%20refering%20to%20the%20two-and-a-half-year%20formula%20for%20ministers%20who%20were%20inducted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWorkers%20are%20not%20slaves.%20I%20am%20not%20needy%2C%20just%20the%20treatment%20was%20not%20good.%20Maharashtra%20is%20on%20the%20path%20of%20Bihar%20because%20we%20are%20not%20looking%20at%20regional%20balance%20but%20caste%20balance%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrakash%20Surve%2C%20the%20MLA%20from%20Magathane%2C%20said%20he%20was%20the%20first%20MLA%20to%20join%20Mr%20Shinde%20after%20the%20rebellion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20a%20simple%20man%2C%20achieved%20everything%20after%20a%20struggle%20and%20will%20continue%20to%20do%20so.%20Many%20who%20demanded%20(cabinet%20berths)%20are%20children%20of%20big%20names%2C%20I%20am%20not.%20Had%20to%20shift%20my%20family%20after%20I%20went%20with%20Shinde%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20murmurs%20of%20protest%20come%20amid%20Mr%20Bawankule's%20assertion%20that%20there%20was%20no%20dispute%20over%20the%20allocation%20of%20cabinet%20portfolios.%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20delay%20in%20allocating%20portfolios%20to%20the%20ministers.%20There%20is%20no%20dispute.%20I%20was%20also%20part%20of%20the%20talks%20and%20the%20matter%20stands%20finished.%20There%20is%20no%20dispute%20and%20it%20will%20be%20announced%20soon%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Bawankule