n%3Cp%3EZakirbhai%20entered%20the%20room%2C%20curious%20about%20who%20was%20playing%20his%20instrument.%20He%20asked%2C%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3EAapko%20bajana%20hai%3F%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E(Do%20you%20want%20to%20play%20it%3F)%C2%A0With%20innocent%20determination%2C%20I%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BYes.%26quot%3B%20Smiling%2C%20he%20sat%20me%20on%20his%20lap%2C%20placed%20my%20tiny%20hands%20on%20the%20Tabla%2C%20and%20showed%20me%20how%20to%20play.%20Little%20did%20I%20know%20that%20this%20moment%20would%20forever%20change%20my%20life.%20Ustad%20Zakir%20Hussain%20became%20the%20first%20to%20place%20my%20hands%20on%20the%20Tabla%2C%20setting%20me%20on%20a%20path%20of%20musical%20devotion%20and%20excellence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYears%20later%2C%20at%20the%20age%20of%2011%2C%20I%20had%20the%20courage%20to%20ask%20my%20Gurus%2C%20Ustad%20Alla%20Rakha%20and%20Ustad%20Zakir%20Hussain%2C%20to%20be%20strict%20with%20me%2C%20to%20expect%20the%20highest%20standards%2C%20and%20to%20train%20me%20with%20discipline%20so%20that%20I%20could%20strive%20to%20be%20the%20best.%20Their%20guidance%20was%20rigorous%20yet%20nurturing%2C%20shaping%20me%20into%20the%20musician%20I%20am%20today.%20Their%20wealth%20of%20knowledge%20and%20their%20exacting%20nature%20taught%20me%20the%20significance%20of%20discipline%2C%20precision%20and%20dedication%20to%20my%20craft.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhen%20I%20First%20Performed%20With%20'Zakirbhai'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20first%20performance%20with%20Zakirbhai%20at%20the%20age%20of%2015%20holds%20a%20very%20special%20place%20in%20my%20heart%20for%20the%20incredible%20learnings%20I%20received.%20Initially%2C%20I%20thought%20I%20was%20merely%20accompanying%20him%20on%20his%20travels.%20To%20my%20astonishment%2C%20he%20informed%20me%20that%20I%20would%20perform%20with%20a%20Kathak%20dancer%20in%20his%20stead%20as%20he%20had%20to%20leave%20due%20to%20an%20urgent%20commitment.%20I%20practised%20all%20night%20with%20the%20Kathak%20artiste%20to%20prepare%20for%20the%20show.%20The%20next%20day%2C%20he%20surprised%20me%20again%2C%20choosing%20to%20stay%20and%20inviting%20me%20to%20accompany%20him%20during%20his%20Tabla%20solo.%20When%20I%20asked%20him%20which%20%3Cem%3Etaal%3C%2Fem%3E%20he%20intended%20to%20present%2C%20he%20smiled%20and%20asked%20my%20age.%20%26quot%3BFifteen%26quot%3B%20I%20replied.%20So%20he%20chose%20to%20perform%20a%2015-matra%20Pancham%20Sawari%20Taal%2C%20a%20complex%20rhythm%20cycle%20I%20had%20never%20even%20heard%20before.%20At%20that%20moment%2C%20I%20learned%20to%20be%20quick-witted%2C%20to%20adapt%2C%20to%20think%20on%20my%20feet%2C%20be%20prepared%20to%20deal%20with%20any%20exigency%20and%20be%20flexible%20to%20work%20with%20any%20musician%20or%20genre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Ustad%20Zakir%20%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Ustad%20Zakir%20%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fqqmmsav_zakir-hussain_625x300_16_December_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20author%20with%20Ustad%20Zakir%20Hussain.%20Courtesy%3A%20Pt%20Anuradha%20Pal%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20vividly%20remember%20accompanying%20him%20to%20late-night%20concerts.%20After%20dinner%2C%20we%20would%20sit%20together%20and%20he%20would%20ask%20me%20for%20an%20analysis%20of%20his%20performance.%20While%20I%20felt%20I%20was%20in%20no%20position%20to%20judge%20such%20a%20great%20master%2C%20this%20was%20actually%20his%20style%20of%20teaching%E2%80%94ensuring%20I%20was%20paying%20attention%2C%20being%20quick-witted%20and%20staying%20attuned%20to%20every%20nuance.%20Then%2C%20he%20would%20recite%20a%20composition%20just%20once%20and%20then%20tell%20me%20he%20expected%20it%20to%20be%20perfected%20by%20the%20next%20morning.%20These%20formative%20experiences%20under%20his%20guidance%20have%20been%20invaluable%20to%20my%20growth%20as%20a%20musician.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Are%20You%20Still%20Practising'%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20cherished%20memory%20is%20when%20he%20taught%20me%20the%20importance%20of%20balance%20between%20the%20left%20and%20right%20hand%20on%20the%20Tabla.%20He%20asked%20me%20to%20practise%20the%20simple%20Theka%20of%20Teen%20Taal%20for%20a%20couple%20of%20hours%20and%20nothing%20else%20until%20he%20returned.%20I%20practised%20diligently%20all%20day%2C%20but%20he%20didn't%20return%20until%20quite%20late.%20I%20came%20back%20the%20next%20day%20and%20repeated%20the%20exercise.%20On%20the%20third%20day%2C%20he%20finally%20appeared%20and%20asked%20quizzically%2C%20%26quot%3BAre%20you%20still%20practising%20this%3F%26quot%3B%20When%20I%20told%20him%20that%20I%20was%2C%20he%20smiled%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BGood.%20Let's%20have%20lunch%20together%2C%20and%20then%20I'll%20see%20what%20you've%20practised.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZakirbhai%20was%20the%20inspirational%20powerhouse%20behind%20several%20of%20my%20innovative%20creations%3A%20%3Cem%3EStree%20Shakti%3C%2Fem%3E%20(India's%20first%20all-girl%20band)%2C%20%3Cem%3ERamayan%20on%20Tabla%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3ETabla%20Jugalbandi%3C%2Fem%3E.%20In%20fact%2C%20my%20fusion%20albums%2C%20%3Cem%3EGet%20Recharged%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3ERecharge%20Plus%3C%2Fem%3E%20are%20all%20dedicated%20to%20him%20because%20of%20the%20way%20he%20made%20percussion%20an%20additional%20voice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20yearly%20Tabla%20retreats%20in%20the%20US%20were%20a%20goldmine%20of%20knowledge.%20In%20just%20one%20week%2C%20he%20would%20impart%20so%20much%20wisdom%20that%20it%20would%20take%20an%20entire%20year%20to%20assimilate%20and%20practice%20what%20he%20had%20taught.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20me%2C%20Zakirbhai%20was%20not%20just%20a%20Guru%20but%20also%20an%20elder%20brother%2C%20who%20I%20cherished%20tying%20Rakhi%20to%20every%20year.%20He%20had%20an%20incredible%20sense%20of%20humour%2C%20a%20treasure%20trove%20of%20anecdotes%2C%20and%20an%20innate%20ability%20to%20make%20learning%20joyful.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3