eeing%20to%20it%20without%20any%20bitterness%2C%26quot%3B%20Shukla%20told%20PTI%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2Cnofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.news18.com%2Fcricket%2Ffocus-on-players-safety-cant-send-them-to-pak-bcci-vp-rajeev-shukla-hopes-for-amicable-solution-to-champions-trophy-tussle-ws-b-9157422.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENews18%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20focus%20is%20majorly%20on%20our%20players'%20safety%20and%20hence%20we%20cannot%20send%20them%20to%20Pakistan.%20We%20are%20looking%20for%20a%20middle%20ground%20to%20sort%20things%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20Pakistan%20Cricket%20Board's%20(PCB)%20decision%20to%20accept%20to%20host%20the%20Champions%C2%A0Trophy%202025%20in%20a%20hybrid%20format%20following%20India's%20refusal%20to%20travel%20across%20the%20border%20has%20caused%20discontent%20in%20the%20organisation%20with%20sources%20telling%20IANS%20that%20many%20members%20are%20unhappy%20with%20the%20way%20Pakistan%20has%20accepted%20the%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20International%20Cricket%20Council%20(ICC)%20has%20confirmed%20a%20proposal%20for%20a%20hybrid%20model%20for%20the%C2%A0Champions%C2%A0Trophy%C2%A02025%20in%20which%20India%20will%20play%20their%20matches%20in%20Dubai%20while%20Pakistan%20will%20host%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20tournament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20compensation%2C%20Pakistan%20has%20been%20allowed%20to%20play%20their%20matches%20in%20the%202026%20T20%20World%20Cup%20in%20Colombo.%20Pakistan%20has%20also%20been%20allotted%20the%20hosting%20rights%20for%20an%20ICC%20women's%20event%20after%202027.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(With%20IANS%20inputs)%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734358680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fkq6tcivo_india-pakistan-match_625x300_18_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fcant-send-them-to-pakistan-bcci-sends-big-bitt