E2%80%99s%20an%20even%20more%20insidious%20impact%3A%20the%20social%20stigma.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F212728%2Fpadmashri-winner-2020-usha-chaumar-manual-scavenging-india-untouchability-say143%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EManual%20scavengers%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20often%20ostracised%2C%20their%20dignity%20eroded%20by%20a%20society%20that%20deems%20their%20work%20impure.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20those%20engaged%20in%20this%20work%20are%20often%20left%20with%20little%20hope%20for%20better%20job%20prospects%20or%20social%20mobility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20what%20if%20technology%20could%20end%20not%20just%20the%20physical%20danger%20of%20this%20work%2C%20but%20also%20the%20centuries-old%20stigma%20attached%20to%20it%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKerala-based%20startup%20Genrobotics%20promises%20to%20answer%20this%20question%20with%20Bandicoot%20%E2%80%94%20a%20machine%20designed%20to%20eliminate%20manual%20scavenging.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20robotic%20solution%20to%20a%20dehumanising%20problem%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFounded%20by%20four%20engineers%20%E2%80%94%20Arun%20George%2C%20Nikhil%20NP%2C%20Rashid%20K%2C%20and%20Govind%20MK%20%E2%80%94%20Genrobotics%E2%80%99%20flagship%20innovation%2C%20the%20Bandicoot%20robot%2C%20is%20named%20after%20a%20species%20of%20rats%20which%20is%20known%20to%20dig%20and%20live%20in%20tunnels%20underground.%20It%20is%20specifically%20designed%20to%20clean%20sewers%2C%20septic%20tanks%2C%20and%20manholes%20without%20the%20need%20for%20manual%20labour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bandicoot%20robot%20is%20designed%20to%20operate%20in%20narrow%2C%20confined%20spaces%2C%20which%20are%20typically%20difficult%20and%20dangerous%20for%20humans%20to%20navigate%20and%20consists%20of%20two%20main%20components%3A%20a%20stand%20unit%20and%20a%20robotic%20drone%20unit.%20The%20drone%20unit%20is%20lowered%20into%20the%20manhole%2C%20