tage%20like%20Cannes.%20She%20began%20her%20speech%20in%20Bangla%20before%20switching%20to%20English%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sayan%20fondly%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20film%E2%80%99s%20poster%20and%20teaser%20were%20also%20launched%20at%20Cannes%2C%20and%20Sayan%20recounts%20the%20surreal%20moment%20when%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F133350%2Fbhanu-athaiya-unsung-woman-won-indias-1st-oscar-long-ar-rahman%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20R%20Rahman%3C%2Fa%3E%20promoted%20the%20film.%20%E2%80%9CAs%20someone%20from%20the%20music%20industry%2C%20having%20Rahman%20acknowledge%20a%20film%20you%20have%20worked%20on%20%E2%80%94%20one%20that%20has%20earned%20international%20acclaim%20%E2%80%94%20is%20surreal%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Sayan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESayan%20stood%20as%20a%20pillar%20of%20constant%20support%20throughout%20the%20film%E2%80%99s%20journey.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20I%20had%20to%20name%20one%20person%20who%20stood%20by%20me%20and%20my%20work%2C%20it%20would%20be%20Sayan%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Indira.%20%E2%80%9CSometimes%2C%20the%20director%2C%20who%20is%20always%20acknowledging%20the%20efforts%20of%20the%20crew%2C%20needs%20appreciation%20too.%20Sayan%20has%20been%20instrumental%20in%20helping%20%3Cem%3EPutul%3C%2Fem%3E%20achieve%20so%20much%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20what%E2%80%99s%20next%2C%20Indira%20is%20already%20working%20on%20a%20new%20Hindi%20project%2C%20a%20biopic%20featuring%20Divya%20Dutta%20and%20Neeraj%20Kabi%2C%20inspired%20by%20the%20works%20of%20legendary%20filmmaker%20Shyam%20Benegal.%20Meanwhile%2C%20%3Cem%3EPutul%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20set%20to%20be%20screened%20in%20the%20United%20States%20in%20December.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20aspiring%20filmmakers%2C%20Indira%20has%20some%20simple%20yet%20powerful%20advice%3A%20%E2%80%9CDon%E2%80%99t%20let%20your%20background%20hold%20you%20back.%20If%20you%20want%20to%20be%20a%20filmmaker%2C%20don%E2%80%99t%20wait%20for%20the%20right%20moment.%20Just%20grab%20a%20camera%2C%20step%20out%20of%20your%20comfort%20zone%2C%20and%20start%20filming.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Khushi%20Arora%3B%20All%20images%20courtesy%20Indira%20Dhar%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734060600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D387993%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Indira%20Dhar%E2%80%99s%20debut%20film%2C%20Putul%2C%20journeyed%20from%20Kolkata%E2%80%99s%20streets%20to%20Cannes%2C%20earning%20a%20standing%20ovation.%20A%20single%20mother%2C%20Indira%20battled%20funding%20struggles%2C%20sold%20her%20jewellery%2C%20and%20balanced%20parenthood%20to%20bring%20this%20powerful%20story%20to%20life.%20Her%20resilience%2C%20rooted%20in%20her%20passion%20for%20storytelling%2C%20turned%20obstacles%20into%20triumphs.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Mervin%20Preethi%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kanpur%20Farmer%20Turns%20Solar-Dried%20Flowers%20Into%20Profits%2C%20Helping%20100%2B%20Local%20Farmers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMotivated%20by%20the%20emerging%20market%20for%20dehydrated%20flowers%2C%20Shivraj%20Nishad%20from%20Kanpur%E2%80%99s%20Shekhpur%20village%20embarked%20on%20a%20remarkable%20journey%20in%202019%20that%20would%20alter%20his%20life%20and%20uplift%20the%20lives%20of%20many%20in%20his%20community.%20Leaving%20his%20job%20as%20a%20pharma%20executive%2C%20the%2032-year-old%20post-grad%20from%20Lucknow%E2%80%99s%20Dr%20A%20P%20J%20Abdul%20Kalam%20Technical%20University%20initiated%20a%20small-scale%20venture%20focused%20on%20cultivating%2C%20harvesting%2C%20and%20dehydrating%20local%20flowers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20earning%20only%20Rs%2021%2C000%2C%20and%20the%20job%20involved%20frequent%20travel%2C%20keeping%20me%20away%20from%20home%20for%20days%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Nishad.%20%E2%80%9CI%20decided%20to%20return%20to%20farming%2C%20but%20rather%20than%20continue%20with%20traditional%20crops%20on%20the%20family%E2%80%99s%20half-acre%20plot%2C%20I%20chose%20to%20grow%20butterfly%20pea%2C%20which%20thrives%20well%20here.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F347227%2Ffarmer-lemon-man-of-raebareli-uttar-pradesh-anand-mishra-earning-five-times-more-in-lakhs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EReturns%20from%20growing%20traditional%20crops%20were%20minimal%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20the%20input%20costs%20were%20high.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20traditional%20crops%20to%20dehydrated%20flowers%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENishad%20began%20his%20venture%20with%20just%2010%20kg%20of%20dehydrated%20flowers%20and%20now%20sells%20between%2020%20and%2030%20tonnes%20annually%2C%20mostly%20sourced%20from%20Shekhpur%20and%20neighbouring%20villages.%20These%20villagers%20were%20traditionally%20growing%20crops%20like%20paddy%2C%20wheat%2C%20and%20lentils.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPreviously%2C%20the%20sale%20of%20fresh%20flowers%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20lucrative%20enough%3B%20if%20they%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20sell%20them%2C%20the%20flowers%20would%20either%20be%20brought%20back%20home%20or%20discarded%20into%20the%20river.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F328701%2Fpunjab-farmer-starts-floriculture-exotic-flowers-help-earn-more-profits%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENishad%20convinced%20the%20farmers%20to%20grow%20these%20flowers%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20sell%20them%20to%20him.%20With%20his%20encouragement%2C%20the%20villagers%20took%20floriculture%20more%20seriously%20and%20now%20grow%20seven%20different%20varieties%20%E2%80%94%20Nishad%20purchases%20their%20entire%20harvest.%20The%20growers%20are%20paid%20promptly%20and%20no%20longer%20have%20to%20travel%2015%20km%20to%20the%20nearest%20%3Cem%3Emandi%20%3C%2Fem%3