%20Ghoramara%2C%20people%20have%20internet%20and%20mobile%20phones%20but%20struggle%20to%20access%20clean%20water%20or%20sanitary%20pads%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Rituporna%2C%20shedding%20light%20on%20the%20gap%20between%20awareness%20of%20wants%20and%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESEED%20emphasises%20the%20pivotal%20role%20of%20education%20in%20the%20development%20of%20the%20Sundarbans.%20%E2%80%9CWithout%20education%2C%20nothing%20can%20develop%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mrinal%20asserts.%20To%20this%20end%2C%20they%20operate%20numerous%20non-formal%20coaching%20centres.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20Sagar%20Island%2C%20we%20have%20a%20school%20dedicated%20only%20to%20the%20Lodha%20tribe.%20They%20are%20first-generation%20learners%20and%20have%20no%20academic%20environment%20in%20their%20households.%20We%20focus%20on%20joyful%20learning%2C%20impart%20knowledge%20through%20dance%20and%20music%2C%20and%20provide%20nutritious%20meals%20to%20invite%20them%20to%20attend%20schools%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Mrinal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20example%2C%2013%20to%2014-year-old%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F284174%2Fmenstruation-periods-girls-school-dropout-whisper%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egirls%20who%20attend%20school%3C%2Fa%3E%20now%20use%20sanitary%20napkins%2C%20which%20are%20disposed%20of%20in%20designated%20bins%20or%20facilities%2C%E2%80%9D%20Soma%20explains%2C%20highlighting%20the%20improved%20quality%20of%20life%20in%20the%20Sundarbans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Arunava%20Banerjee.%20All%20images%20courtesy%20SEED%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733978757000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FMHM-workshop-in-Fatla-1_11zon-1733976579.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D387141%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22For%20almost%20two%20decades%2C%20dedicated%20efforts%20have%20been%20tackling%20t