e%20with%20which%20he%20could%20rehydrate%20them.%20His%20solution%20lay%20in%20the%20butter%20sauce%2C%20which%20eventually%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F356862%2Forigin-story-chicken-tikka-masala-history-shish-mahal-scotland-glasgow-karims-delhi-ranveer-brar-recipe%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egave%20history%20its%20best%20dish%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%201950s%20heyday%2C%20Gujral%E2%80%99s%20Moti%20Mahal%20was%20extremely%20popular%20with%20celebrities%20and%20world%20leaders%2C%20including%20Zakir%20Hussain%2C%20Jawahar%20Lal%20Nehru%2C%20Richard%20Nixon%20and%20John%20F%20Kennedy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fbutter-chicken-in-delhi-3-1733747210.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Moti%20Mahal%20in%20Daryaganj%2C%20Delhi%20was%20the%20birthplace%20of%20the%20butter%20chicken%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fbutter-chicken-in-delhi-3-1733747210.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fbutter-chicken-in-delhi-3-1733747210-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fbutter-chicken-in-delhi-3-1733747210-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fbutter-chicken-in-delhi-3-1733747210-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fbutter-chicken-in-delhi-3-1733747210-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-387679%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EMoti%20Mahal%20in%20Daryaganj%2C%20Delhi%20was%20the%20birthplace%20of%20the%20butter%20chicken%3B%20P