0become%20a%20powerful%20voice%20for%20the%20marginalised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20when%20I%20was%20enrolled%20in%20school%20that%20I%20developed%20a%20sense%20of%20inquisitiveness%20about%20my%20identity.%20I%20would%20be%2C%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20in%20an%20environment%20where%20people%20would%20ask%20me%20my%20full%20name%20and%20where%20I%20was%20from.%20But%20I%20was%20told%20not%20to%20tell%20people%20where%20I%20lived%2C%E2%80%9D%20Naseema%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ELife%20in%20a%20red-light%20district%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENaseema%E2%80%99s%20home%20was%20Chaturbhuj%20Sthan%2C%20a%20red-light%20district%20in%20Muzaffarpur%2C%20Bihar.%20Named%20after%20a%20Vishnu%20temple%2C%20the%20area%20has%20historically%20been%20home%20to%20sex%20workers%20and%20%3Cem%3Etawaifs%3C%2Fem%3E%3B%20its%20religious%20name%20does%20not%20shield%20the%20community%20from%20societal%20stigma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhy%20should%20I%20not%20tell%20people%20who%20I%20am%20and%20where%20I%20come%20from%3F%E2%80%9D%20Naseema%20remembers%20asking%20her%20father%2C%20who%20quickly%20shut%20her%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20girls%20from%20school%20would%20all%20walk%20home%20together%2C%20but%20they%20would%20take%20a%20long%20wounded%20route%20to%20avoid%20my%20%3Cem%3Egully%3C%2Fem%3E.%20They%20were%20told%20to%2C%20so%20I%E2%80%99d%20go%20alone%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20child%2C%20Naseema%20was%20a%20witness%20to%20frequent%20police%20raids%20in%20her%20neighbourhood.%20These%20experiences%20left%20a%20lasting%20impact%2C%20and%20it%20was%20during%20this%20time%20that%20she%20began%20to%20fully%20understand%20the%20marginalisation%20her%20community%20faced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20sr